title: [Ryuketsu] Kill la Kill - 25 (OVA) [PS3/Xbox Compatible-720p]
description:
This is a 720p, hardsubbed, PlayStation/Xbox-compatible release of Ryuketsu's release for the Kill la Kill OVA, a.k.a. episode 25. All translation and subtitling credit goes to Ryuketsu.

There are a small handful of typos in this release, but I didn't catch them until after I'd encoded it, so I hope they don't bother you too much -- because I'm not encoding it again.

If you want to download the original, soft-subbed, 1080p release of this OVA, go here: http://www.nyaa.se/?page=view&tid=594862
